description: Quickly and easily convert between two currencies. Over 150 currencies are supported, and rates are updated hourly. Even has rates for Bitcoin, Silver Ounces, and Gold Ounces.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Currency Converter how much is one bitcoin in united states dollars
Alexa, ask Currency Converter what currencies do you know
Alexa, ask Currency Converter what is the exchange rate for euros
name: Currency Converter
